title: Could Mahomes be best QB ever? - Brady Quinn Football Show (Football 9/25)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and Ryan Wilson to discuss the Redskins decision to stick with Case Keenum at quarterback (4:30), before examining the brilliance of Patrick Mahomes (18:00). The guys then evaluate the performances of several young quarterbacks and project them moving forward including Daniel Jones, Kyle Allen and Mason Rudolph. Brady breaks down Cam Newton's lisfranc injury and what it means for his future (32:30), before examining the state of several desperate teams heading into Week 4 (50:30).
